<!DOCTYPE html>
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/removeemployee.css" />
<div class="jumbotron container">
    <div class="alert alert-info">
        <strong>Lembre-se que qualquer funcionario removido continuará na planilha até o fim do mês. Mas não poderá adicionar nenhum valor durante esse periodo.</strong>
    </div>
    <div class="contatiner">
        <h4>Balconista</h4>
    </div>
    {{#each employees}}
    <div class="container dib-table">
        <div class="col-sm-10">
            {{name}}
        </div>
        <button class="col-sm-2 btn btn-primary employee" id="{{name}}employee" onclick="router_client.event.removeemployee(event)">Remover</button>
    </div>
    {{/each}}

    <hr />

    <div class="contatiner">
        <h4>Vendedor</h4>
    </div>
    {{#each sellers}}
    <div class="container dib-table">
        <div class="col-sm-10">
            {{name}}
        </div>
        <button class="col-sm-2 btn btn-primary seller" id="{{name}}seller" onclick="router_client.event.removeemployee(event)">Remover</button>
    </div>
    {{/each}}
</div>